he (Brahmaa) indeed
नाल-रन्ध्र-अध्वना
through the hollow in the lotus stem
स्व-योग-बल-विध्यया
with the power of his yogic knowledge
स्मवरूढवान्
descended
प्रौढधी: -
he of mighty intellect
त्वदीयम्-अति-मोहनं
Thy this most enchanting
